merald?<br />2.  Do you find it strange that SoE stated they wish they never created the necromancer class?<br />3.  Is Potus merely a pawn for SoE that they use to promote they game?<br />4.  Can the Vision really be this cool?<br />5.  Are the N.E Patriots a dynasty?<br />6.  Why hasn't Verant updated epics?  They are supposed to be EPIC but honestly dropped gear destroys them.<br />7.  EQ2 classless based progression system is based on skills instead of set abilities.  Do you think this will succeed?<br />8.  Is WoW finally going to dethrone the king of MMORPGs or will Everquest remain at the top?<br />9.  If there are froglok necromancers in lower guk, why can't players create one?<br />10. Why are classes still restricted by race?  Why can't I roll up a troll necro?  I know they wouldn't be that good at casting but damn they will be pimp.<br /><br />DISCUSS AWAY my faithful legion.</span id="msg"></font></td>
